The thinkParity taskbar icon is located on the Windows taskbar (usually on the lower right of your screen).

If you close the thinkParity window, you can re-open it by right-clicking on the taskbar icon and selecting 'Open' from the menu. Alternatively, just left-click on the taskbar icon.

To exit thinkParity, right-click on the taskbar icon and select 'Exit' from the menu.